reviewText: Cartoons like this have been forgotten and often neglected, what ever happened to things like this. Zelda and Super Mario Btoehrs were some of the best cartoons ever, they were fantastic, I'm sad that these tapes are so hard to find, but they are fantastic, if you ever see anything from Nintendo please take my advice and buy it, its a must!

This tape has THE best cartoon of my childhood on it. The bad thing is, I've been searching the net for a LONG time and I  haven't found it yet. They're very rare, so if you love it as  much as I do, BUY IT!! or if you don't PLEASE notify me and I'll bargain a reasonable price. My address is grace@UDATA.com
The Legend of Zelda VHS is a great show. It includes the same charaters and story line from the games. This show is action packed and funny.
